original_title: SATOYAMA 体験ツアー第3弾！カントリー・ガールズ と過ごす1泊2日バスツアー in 足利
overview: Is the third SATOYAMA movement fanclub bus tour, featuring Country Girls rather than a SATOYAMA movement unit. It took place on May 30 and 31, 2015 in Ashikaga, Tochigi Prefecture. Disc 1 (61mins), Disc 2 (47mins).
title: SATOYAMA Taiken Tour Dai 3 Dan! Country Girls to Sugosu 1paku 2nichi Bus Tour in Ashikaga
